## рҹҢҝ GIT-WORKFLOW

1. Stelle sicher, dass du noch im Branch `feature/lesson-income-statement-redesign` bist:
```bash
   git branch --show-current
```
2. Falls nicht: `git checkout feature/lesson-income-statement-redesign`
3. Pull falls nГ¶tig: `git pull origin feature/lesson-income-statement-redesign` (falls schon gepusht)
4. Committe weiter in logischen Schritten:
   - `feat(lesson): implement slide 07 pro tips carousel`
   - `feat(lesson): implement slide 08 quiz sort`
   - `feat(lesson): implement slide 09 quiz calc`
   - `feat(lesson): implement slide 10 quiz multi-select`
